fields.name: Living Room
fields.description: A typical Western living room may contain furnishings such as a sofa, chairs, occasional tables, coffee tables, bookshelves, electric lamps, rugs, or other furniture.

fields.name: Bedroom
fields.description: A typical western bedroom contains as bedroom furniture one or two beds (ranging from a crib for an infant, a small twin bed for a single person, twin beds for two people, to a king-size bed for a couple), a clothes closet, a nightstand, and a dresser (dressing table).

fields.name: Dining Room
fields.description: The dining room used to be a place just for eating. Nowadays, it's becoming a place for just about everything that happens at home. With plenty of tables, chairs and storage to choose from, our dining room furniture is designed to help you get more out of your space. More laughter, more talking, more playing, more working – more of all the things you enjoy doing while you're there.

fields.name: Children's Furniture
fields.description: Kids need space to just be kids. Where they can giggle, make believe, hop around – and then settle in for good night's sleep after all that fun. Because that's how they learn and grow and become who they are. That's why all our children's furniture and toys are designed to help you create a safe, creative and comfortable space for your most important people in the world.

fields.name: Bathroom
fields.description: It's a private space for you – that also has to work for everyone else. That has to take care of all your different needs and routines in the same small space (often at the exact same time). That's why we have lots of bathroom furniture that gets smart with storage for every little thing, and helps you make room for feeling refreshed.

fields.name: Apollo 3 Seater Fabric Sofa
fields.description: The 3 Seater sofa is the pinnacle of the Apollo range. Hand made to order the frame which uses solid hardwood, and sumptuous cushions are upholstered in the luxurious Logan fabric. The serpentine spring system improves the weight distribution and longevity in this sofa. As a finishing touch, solid oak feet complete the look of this sofa.

fields.name: Nest of Tables
fields.description: An extremely practical nest of 3 tables made from lacquered, solid Malaysian hardwood and finished with a light oak stain.

fields.name: Upholstered Platform Bed
fields.description: This simple, no-frills platform bed is the perfect addition to an urban chic decor. Upholstered in black faux leather and designed with multiple wooden slats for support, the bed has clean lines and sleek detailing for a trendy look. Designed to not look bulky, this bed is also great for making your space look bigger.
fields.bullet_point_b: Manufactured wood, faux leather and metal
fields.bullet_point_c: Metal side rails and center rails for guaranteed stability and durability

fields.name: Nancy Upholstered Platform Bed
fields.description: This faux leather platform bed will update your entire bedroom. It ships in one carton with the frame, legs and wooden slats conveniently located in the zippered compartment in the back of the headboard for easy assembly. This espresso faux leather platform bed features a headboard and low profile footboard style frame, with wood slats and exposed feet for support. This contemporary platform bed makes an excellent addition to any bedroom.
fields.bullet_point_c: Not recommended to use a sleep number bed with the bed
fields.bullet_point_d: Memory foam mattress can be used
fields.bullet_point_e: Cannot be used without the headboard

fields.name: Deluxe Contemporary Personalized Kids Recliner with Storage Compartment
fields.description: Kids will now be able to enjoy the comfort that adults experience with a comfortable recliner that was made just for them! Personalize this recliner with child's name for a personal touch. This chair features a strong wood frame with soft foam and then enveloped in durable vinyl upholstery for your active child. Choose from an array of colors that will best suit your child's personality or bedroom. This petite sized recliner features storage arms so kids can store items away and retrieve at their convenience.

fields.name: Children's 5 Piece Square Table and Chair Set
fields.description: The children's folding table with folding legs and 4 folding child sized chairs set is a must have for every parent and grandparent. These wonderful chairs have push button safety locks, padded seats for comfortable sitting, and the table folds up for convenient and easy storage. Children love the fun colors, and parents love the portability.
fields.bullet_point_a: Set includes blue table and 1 each of red, blue, green and yellow chairs
fields.bullet_point_b: Child sized table with folding legs and 4 child sized folding chairs
fields.bullet_point_c: Chairs are padded and fold up for convenience and portability
fields.bullet_point_d: Table has folding legs for easy storage and have rubber caps on the bottom of the legs
fields.bullet_point_e: Sturdy, durable, and fun for the kids

fields.name: Salem's Bookcase
fields.description: Arrange framed photos and books in the study or toys and craft supplies in the playroom on this understated bookcase, featuring an understated silhouette and multi-colored finish.
fields.bullet_point_a: Bring organization and creativity to your child’s bedroom with the Jennifer storage bookcase
fields.bullet_point_b: Practice shapes, spelling or just doodle on the front chalkboard panel of the cubby (chalk and eraser not included)
fields.bullet_point_c: Stack toys, books, or decorative items on the 3 open shelves
fields.bullet_point_d: Store shoes, clothing and toys in the large bottom cubby
fields.bullet_point_e: Sturdy back panel provides extra stability and lasting support

fields.name: Weldon's Kids' Bookcase
fields.description: Weldon's Kids’ Bookcase is an elegant way to display and organize your child’s or teen’s room. 4 spacious shelves provide room for all your child’s books, as well as toys, movies, music, photos and other personal items. Tested for children ages 4 and up. Bookshelf requires assembly upon delivery.
fields.bullet_point_a: Curved side panels make this bookcase safe for your children, but also visually interesting and upscale
fields.bullet_point_d: Bottom compartment creates a bin that is great for storing larger toys and shoes
fields.bullet_point_e: Eye catching silhouette of the Cosco Mia Kids’ 4 Shelf Bookcase will look great in any child’s or teen’s room

fields.name: Marise's Writing Desk
fields.description:
Enhance the aesthetic appeal of your child's bedroom Marise's Writing Desk. It has a contemporary style that blends in with the existing home decor.

The wood is available in a soft white finish that adds a touch of beauty to the home decor. This desk has an open cabinet, which is ideal for storing books and toys. The desk comes equipped with a drawer that provides additional space to accommodate your storage needs. This drawer has a wooden knob that adds to its style-quotient. The drawer glide is made from metal to ensure sturdiness. Your child can comfortably work on this desk, due to the ample leg space. This desk is made from non-toxic materials, which makes it safe to use in home with children. It is eco-friendly, making it the ideal selection for people who care about the environment.
fields.bullet_point_b: One open storage bin with identification plate
fields.bullet_point_c: Intended for use in the bedroom

fields.name: Little Princess's 2 Piece Vanity Set with Mirror
fields.description: The Little Princess's 2 Piece Vanity Set with Mirror is a great choice for your child’s dressing room. This vanity set includes a beautifully crafted vanity table and a matching stool. It also includes an oval-shaped mirror. This vanity set is a functional and ornamental addition to your child’s room. Constructed from MDF, this vanity set is sturdy and durable. It is enameled with a pink and white finish. The drawers in this vanity table can be utilized for keeping the knick-knacks of your children. Requires assembly. The surface of this vanity set is water resistant, and it has an eco-friendly design that causes no damage to the environment.
fields.bullet_point_a: Hand carved design with durable wooden construction designed by Teamson Design Corp
fields.bullet_point_b: Perfect place for your kids learning and entertainment activities
fields.bullet_point_c: Table/Chair legs made by real wood, not by MDF to keep construction more sturdy

fields.name: Fez 6 Piece Towel Set
fields.description: The zero twist weave of these towels allows the water to be absorbed very quickly, while the combed cotton ensures durability. The uniform loops give the towels a luxurious, plush look and feel; while the design conveys fashion and sophistication.
fields.bullet_point_a: Includes: 2 Bath towels, 2 hand towels and 2 washcloths

fields.name: Drift Rectangular 6 Seater Dining Table
fields.description:
This elegant dining table boasts quaint charm in its delicate design. Made from a mixture of mindy ash solids and veneers and alabasia wood, it’s sturdy and hard wearing. Seats 6. Pair with the Drift dining chairs or bench to complete the look.

This elegant range exudes quaint charm with its delicate, traditional designs. The muted colours will complement a variety of decors while panelled finishes and rustic metal detailing creates a breezy, coastal-inspired look. These attractive-yet-unassuming features lends the collection especially well to casual, everyday entertaining.

Reimagining heritage style with a fresh twist, Modern Country is inspired by the beautiful gardens at the Leckford Estate, our working farm in Hampshire. Discover painterly florals and botanical prints in subtle shades, as well as a range of contemporary farmhouse furniture.

fields.name: Ambrine Upholstered Bedroom Bench
fields.description: Adorned with elegant nailhead trim and featuring a timeless tufted top, this lovely bench brings a pop of glamour to your space. Try setting it in the entryway topped with a fur throw for a bold accent, or add it to the foot of your bed to bring eye-catching appeal to the master suite.

fields.name: Light Blue Area Rug
fields.description: This Turkish Ford rug is made of polypropylene. This rug is easy-to-clean, stain resistant, and does not shed

fields.name: Black leather dining chair
fields.description: Each chair in this set features a plush seat cushion along with a tufted back, which ensures maximum comfort while you are dining. The crown shaped top of these chairs adds charm to their appearance.  As these chairs are available in a variety of colors, you can make a selection as per your taste or requirements.
fields.bullet_point_a: Plush seat cushion for maximum comfort
fields.bullet_point_c: Sturdy hardwood frame for stability and years of use
fields.bullet_point_d: Useful in the dining room or any other room as comfortable additional seating

fields.name: 5 Piece Dining Set
fields.description: Anchor the dining room in effortless style with this essential set, perfect for weekday meals and family gatherings alike.
fields.bullet_point_a: Set includes table and four chairs

fields.name: Over the Toilet Storage
fields.description: This 3-tiered bathroom shelf offers storage and style. Ideal for small bathrooms, this contemporary shelf takes advantage of vertical space to create room to organize towels, toiletries, and more bathroom essentials.

fields.name: Reversible Stripe Bath Rug
fields.description: Keep your decor fresh with the reversible rug. Made of 100% cotton, the rug is durable and easy to clean. Featuring two sides of stripes. Machine washable.

fields.name: 6 Drawer Dresser
fields.description: This dresser was designed with clean, straight lines and features six spacious drawers mounted on metal slides for smooth gliding. The drawers are fitted with modern cut outs instead of handles, making it an easy match to all décor types.
fields.bullet_point_a: Cut-out handles at the top of the drawers
fields.bullet_point_b: Decorative kick plate which adds to its contemporary style

fields.name: Novelty Table Lamp
fields.description: Brimming with distinctive style, the Novelty Table Lamp is an eye-catching addition to your decor collection. Its design is inspired by paint pouring out of bucket, while its solid color pattern blends effortlessly into any space. Use it to round out your little one's room in whimsical style, then pair it with a vintaged framed print for a dynamic look. Match it with a minimalist design to accentuate its charming silhouette or add it to a bold boho display for a complementing look. Equally at home in your little one's room or adding playful style to the den, this statement-making table lamp elevates any space in your home.

fields.name: Vanity Set with Mirror
fields.description: This stylish vanity set will be a lovely addition to you casual master bedroom or dressing area, adding subtle charm and a touch of comfort. The simply styled piece features metal construction in a black finish, which will blend nicely with any decor. The vanity has a glass top, for a sophisticated look, accommodating your essentials like perfume and hair care products. The lower glass shelf offers additional space to stash a magazine, or make-up. Simple tube legs support the vanity, while a swirly heart motif at each side adds a pretty touch. A swivel mirror is attached to the top of this vanity, to reflect light and help you get ready for your day, featuring a heart detail at the crown for a cheerful accent. The matching stool repeats the heart motif, and features a luxurious black fabric padded seat, for the perfect finishing touch. Add this wonderful vanity set to your home to complete your casual master bedroom ensemble.

fields.name: Living Room Barrel Arm Chair
fields.description: Stylish armchair to accompany any living room decor.

fields.name: Extra Wide Width Blackout Thermal Single Curtain Panel
fields.description: Blackout curtains features an innovative fabric construction for single layer blackout. Unlike blackout curtains with stiff lining, Best Home Fashion curtains are extremely soft and drapable. Wide width curtains are perfect for large windows and patio doors.

fields.name: Extra Wide Width Blackout Thermal Single Curtain Panel
fields.description: Blackout curtains features an innovative fabric construction for single layer blackout. Unlike blackout curtains with stiff lining, Best Home Fashion curtains are extremely soft and drapable. Wide width curtains are perfect for large windows and patio doors.

fields.name: Reclaimed Pine Wood Dining Table
fields.description: This reclaimed pine wood table makes the perfect anchor to your cottage-chic dining room or kitchen. Complement the white wash finish with neutral-hued chairs and then top it with a blooming vase for a touch of classic appeal.

fields.name: Wall Mirror
fields.description: Brimming with classic appeal, this wall mirror effortlessly refreshes any room. Create an eye-catching focal point in the entryway with bold giclee prints and shimmering mirrors and accents.

fields.name: 4 Light Globe Pendant
fields.description: Blending factory influences with cosmopolitan cool, this chic pendant transforms any room into a stylish loft. Showcasing an openwork design, this geometric luminary is perfect hanging in a pair above the foyer or dining table. Cast an inviting glow in your foyer or dining room with this elegant pendant, showcasing a candelabra-inspired design and distressed details.
fields.bullet_point_c: Not recommended for use in a bathroom

fields.name: Wall Mounted Cabinet
fields.description:
Wall Mount Cabinet takes care of all your bathroom storage needs. The cabinet allows you to store or stack up all necessary bathroom materials that you might need. The traditional style of the cabinet blends well with most bathroom decors.

The Wall Mount Cabintet features a wood construction that makes it strong and durable. The cabinet has an open shelf and closed storage that offers multiple storage options. The shelf can be used to store items like a small clock or soaps and shampoos. The closed storage is ideal to stack up clean towels or bunch of toilet papers. The plastic door pulls adds style to the doors and makes it easy to use. The towel rack provided with the cabinet holds one or more towels comfortably.
fields.bullet_point_a: Wall cabinet with full width towel bar
fields.bullet_point_c: Includes all the hardware to put it together

fields.name: 1 Light Bathroom Wall Sconce
fields.description: The Design House Bathroom Wall Sconce features a modern design and a galvanized steel finish with a wire shade. This sconce can be used for bathroom, hallway or foyer lighting. The wall sconce offers reliable lighting with an industrial design. This model uses (1) 60 Watt medium base incandescent bulb (A19 Bulb type). Wall sconce is designed for wall mount applications. Metal cage measures 8.23" x 6.76. This unit is ETL/cETL Listed and suitable for indoor use. The Design House Bathroom Wall Sconce comes with a 10-year limited warranty.
fields.bullet_point_b: Modern design with a metal wire shade
fields.bullet_point_c: Wall mount applications for bathroom or hallway lighting
fields.bullet_point_d: Bulb type: 60W Medium base A19 type bulb

fields.name: Banana Leaves Shower Curtain
fields.description: Shower curtain in 100% woven poly oxford with printed front and buttonhole openings.
